DIMENSIONS AND UNITS
7 fundamental dimensions
	- length
	- mass
	- time
	- temperature
	- electric current
	- amount of substance
	- luminous intensity

SI base unit
	- length - meter - m
	- mass - kilogram - kg
	- time - second - s
	- temperature - kelvin - K
	- current - ampere - A
	- amount - mole - mol
